{"tid":581714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[開心大發現］去日本自駕遊慳錢方法","createTime":"2018-03-05T14:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T14:38:52.000Z","uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a15496c0cfc820a41a97e1e52a80762f3db9b49f","tid":581714,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:35:23.000Z","msg":"原來日文網會比中文版本平好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下就係我個人經驗<br />\n<br />\nTabirai 應該大部分人去日本自駕遊都係經呢個網<br />\n因為點計佢都係最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n神奇嘅事就發生喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/223031_a98e300a1be0fe910d267da39338dc7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F223031_a98e300a1be0fe910d267da39338dc7e.png&h=5439e62e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我喺中文版網站搵到嘅價錢<br />\n咁然後多手去日文版睇睇啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/223128_260c42dd2caecbf93ff9250e7c501306.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F223128_260c42dd2caecbf93ff9250e7c501306.png&h=00fdd565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHi!Auntie!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣日子 同樣地方 同一間公司<br />\n竟然會有唔同價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算我用日文版訂晒 買埋保險都仲要平過中文版網站嘅乜都唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以大家以後去日本租車嗰陣 知點做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09949e7ce385facf582c3939e23fe086a15454d","tid":581714,"uid":204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"有d 特別版既pass 專for 遊車一樣唔會比你係日文版成功book 到"},{"pid":"fdbfe7ba56ce0f4a5c498f6bbe21c310b656e9f6","tid":581714,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"不嬲架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日文版有得簡車款添"}]}